FastWeb Fourth-Quarter Net Loss Widens From Year Earlier as Revenue Falls

-- B y   D a n   L i e f g r e e n   a n d   F r a n c e s c a   C i n e l l i
-- 
2011-02-17T06:44:48Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-17/fastweb-fourth-quarter-net-loss-widens-from-year-earlier-as-revenue-falls.html
  FastWeb SpA  said it had a fourth-
quarter net loss of 83.1 million euros, compared with a loss of
64.9 million euros in the same period a year earlier. Revenue
fell to 475 million euros from 487.6 million euros a year
earlier, the company said in a statement distributed by the
Italian Exchange.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dan Liefgreen at 
 dliefgreen@bloomberg.net  